OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FThe
OL,6,Fsmall chance of a shower on Saturday
OL,7,Fafternoon, otherwise a dry weekend and
OL,8,Fearly part to next week. Often sunny
OL,9,Fwith some cloud likely at times.
OL,10,FTurning much warmer.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
